description: This Chainlink VRF top 2% rating Sakura purrs with a rating of 86, and a multiplier of 1x. It has a total score of 86, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
